name: Qr00_Base_Prospect_N_importune_TMKT3
queryText:
SELECT B.CPF,
      CASE WHEN B.VALIDA_NAO_IMPORTUNE = 1 AND N3.TELEFONE IS NOT NULL OR Nao_Importune = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS Nao_Importune
FROM TB_BASE_PROSPECT_COMOTC_TRATADA_TMKT B 
INNER JOIN TB_BASE_NAO_IMPORTUNE N3 ON ISNULL(CONCAT(DDD_03, TEL_03), '00000000000') = LTRIM(RTRIM(N3.TELEFONE))
